	<h3>Related Documents</h3>      
	<ul>
	
	<li><a href="/en/employment/unemployment_and_redundancy/redundancy/redundancy_procedures.html">Redundancy procedures</a><br>There are a number of procedures employers must follow when making staff redundant. Find out about these procedures and how your rights are set down in law.</li>
	
	<li><a href="/en/employment/unemployment_and_redundancy/redundancy/redundancy.html">Qualifying for redundancy</a><br>If you lose your job you may be eligible for redundancy. What are the rules on qualifying for a redundancy payment.</li>
	
	<li><a href="/en/employment/unemployment_and_redundancy/redundancy/lay_off_short_time_working_and_redundancy.html">Lay off, short-time working and redundancy</a><br>Employees who have in a lay-off or short-time working situation may be entitled to a redundancy payment. Find out more.</li>
	
